 in the heat of battle with a mouse designed to play the long game. *May vary depending on usage conditions</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">RAZER 5G ADVANCED 18K OPTICAL SENSOR &mdash; Tailor the mouse to the playstyle with a new, robust set of sensitivity settings. Enjoy responsive, pixel-precise aim with an ultra-reliable sensor that tracks movement with zero spinouts</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">RAZER MECHANICAL MOUSE SWITCHES GEN-2 &mdash; With new gold-plated contact points, the switches are less prone to degrading and have a longer lifespan of up to 60-million clicks, so gamers can enjoy crisp execution that&rsquo;s just as consistent</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">POWERED BY RAZER CHROMA RGBL: Customize from 16.8 million colors and countless lighting effects, and experience greater immersion as the mouse reacts dynamically with hundreds of Chroma-integrated games</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">#1 SELLING PC GAMING PERIPHERALS BRAND IN THE U.S. &mdash; Source &mdash; Circana, Retail Tracking Service, U.S., Dollar Sales, Gaming Designed Mice, Keyboards, and PC Headsets, Jan. 2019- Dec. 2023 combined</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">OPTIMIZE MOUSE ACCURACY &mdash; Improve accuracy by disabling the \"Enhance pointer precision\" option in the Windows mouse settings, and further optimize performance using the Razer Synapse App</span></li>\r\n</ul>','/upload/fbce9a8f-fcdc-4064-a59d-3bee84c40a5117535291519236.jpg','Razer Basilisk V3 X HyperSpeed Customizable Wireless Gaming Mouse',1100000,16,'razer-basilisk-v3-x-hyperspeed-customizable-wireless-gaming-mouse',0,_binary '',1),(24,'<div id=\"featurebullets_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget\" data-feature-name=\"featurebullets\" data-csa-c-type=\"widget\" data-csa-c-content-id=\"featurebullets\" data-csa-c-slot-id=\"featurebullets_feature_div\" data-csa-c-asin=\"B0DT15Z62M\" data-csa-c-is-in-initial-active-row=\"false\" data-csa-c-id=\"hf24ur-vwokon-gs4zkx-hhplb2\" data-cel-widget=\"featurebullets_feature_div\">\r\n<div id=\"feature-bullets\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-medium a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\">\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Triple Connectivity: SM809 Pro wireless MMO gaming mouse supports tri mode connection(2.4GHz/BT5.0/Type C wired).It can save the settings of up to 4 devices and is compatible with devices such as desktop computers,laptops,smartphones and tablets.You can quickly switch between different connections by pressing the mode switch button at the bottom of the mouse.The operation is convenient and the switching is fast</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">High-Precision Sensor: SM809 Pro wireless gaming mouse with side buttons is equipped with a high performance PAW3311 optical sensor,boasting low latency and exceptional precision.This MMO mouse allows you to fine adjust the DPI from 100 to 24000 (&plusmn;20%),the polling rate up to 1000Hz,tracking speed 300IPS,acceleration 35G.Whether you\'re performing precise maneuvers or making rapid movements,this gaming mouse offers unparalleled accuracy,ensuring that every in game command is flawlessly translated onto the screen</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Ergonomic Design:SM809 Pro wireless gaming mouse is designed with comfort in mind.The honeycomb shell design is more breathable,sweat resistant and lightweight,which can reduce hand fatigue.Its ergonomic design with a 90&deg; arched curve perfectly fits larger hands,offering a more comfortable grip.The SM809 MMO mouse has a reinforced internal structure,durable materials and smooth mouse feet pads, ensuring that the mouse can withstand frequent clicks and glide smoothly,providing players with a smooth and responsive gaming experience</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Customization for Personalized Experience:The SM809 Pro MMO mouse comes with 4 interchangeable magnetic side panels(3 buttons side/9 buttons side panel/figure rest side panel/regular side panel). Replacing these accessories is smooth and convenient.Users can replace the mouse accessories according to their own preferences to achieve personalized customization.Through the exclusive software,users can reset button functions,complex macro files,adjust DPI and adjust RGB lighting. The comprehensive programmability and customizability of the macro mouse enable the creation of a fully customized gaming and working environment, making your experience more enriching and interesting.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Intelligent Power Management:The intelligent power saving design of the SM809 Pro wireless gaming mouse ensures long lasting battery life.The energy saving mode is set as the default at the factory.When the mouse is moved,the RGB lights turn off automatically to reduce power consumption.However,users can enable the constant lighting mode through the software.It should be noted that enabling this mode will increase power consumption,if you more like constant lighting mode,It is recommended to use a wired connection to ensure an uninterrupted gaming experience</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"productDetailsVoyagerAccordion_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget\" data-feature-name=\"productDetailsVoyagerAccordion\" data-csa-c-type=\"widget\" data-csa-c-content-id=\"productDetailsVoyagerAccordion\" data-csa-c-slot-id=\"productDetailsVoyagerAccordion_feature_div\" data-csa-c-asin=\"B0DT15Z62M\" data-csa-c-is-in-initial-active-row=\"false\" data-csa-c-id=\"jfyob0-jw31j1-pucm6g-qb6s8n\" data-cel-widget=\"productDetailsVoyagerAccordion_feature_div\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"provenanceCertifications_feature_div\" class=\"celw