fect hand feel, gives gamers the most comfortable gaming experienece and makes you feel free from fatigue.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Wide Compatibility Support Windows XP, Vista, Windows 7, Windows 8. Adaptable for Notebook, PC, laptop, Computer, Macbook and so on.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','/upload/8750640b-3fd9-484d-addd-9c326954a4a8175352953530510.png','Alienware 610M Wired/Wireless Gaming Mouse (AW610M)',1400000,17,'alienware-610m-wiredwireless-gaming-mouse-aw610m',0,_binary '',1),(26,'<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\">\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Three Ways to Game: Connect with hyper-fast, sub-1ms SLIPSTREAM CORSAIR WIRELESS TECHNOLOGY, low-latency Bluetooth, or USB wired.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Comfort When It Counts: Contoured shape that&rsquo;s sculpted specifically for palm-grips and larger hands.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Powerfully Precise Optical Gaming Sensor: A custom Pixart PMW3391 native 18,000 DPI sensor, adjustable in 1 DPI resolution steps, gives you total sensitivity customization and ultra-accurate tracking.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Ten Fully Programmable Buttons: Customize the way you play with powerful macros and key remaps to give you an in-game advantage.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Ultra-Durable Omron Switches: Rated for more than 50 million clicks.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Dynamic, Three-Zone RGB Backlighting: Choose from dozens of customizable presets and effects to perfectly match your setup.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','/upload/bd5ba2f7-f182-4801-8963-de94a734de62175352980102711.jpg','CORSAIR IRONCLAW WIRELESS RGB Rechargeable Gaming Mouse',1000000,18,'corsair-ironclaw-wireless-rgb-rechargeable-gaming-mouse',0,_binary '',1),(27,'<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\">\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">3 Mode Connectivity:SM802 gaming mouse supports 2.4G wireless, BT5.0 and wired 3 connection modes.It can be save 4 devices same time,fast response and smooth operation.NOTE!!Use the wireless function, please switch the mouse\'s signal source to the signal light corresponding and device,otherwise it will not be connected</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">DIY Personalized Hotswap Mouse: SM802 wireless mouse is a DIY-able personalized mouse that comes with 2 sets of micro switches (gaming switch and office mute switch) by default. Users can change different types of microswitches by themselves according to their needs, and it is also compatible with most of the branded microswitches in the market</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">1 Mouse 4 Styles: SM802 custom mouse comes with 2 sets of shells (hollowed-out shell and classic shell), which can be combined into 4 styles of gaming mice! If users purchase SM802 of different colors, can combine more unique styles ! The hollow design shell with RGB lighting enhances the gaming atmosphere, and the classic shell is more versatile</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Custom and 7 Programmable Buttons: SM802 computer mouse supports software customization.Through the software users can reset the button functions, adjust DPI, configure macro files, etc.The custom software functions only supports Windows system and wired mode</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Adjustable DPI and Battery Rechargeable:SM802 rechargeable RGB mouse can be adjusted within 6 levels DPI(1000,1200,1600,2400,4800,10000); Built-in 450Mah lithium battery, with USB-C charging cable. Low battery indicator will flashing red light. It also supported recharged while using, not afraid of power off in gaming</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Power Saving Design: SM802 wireless gaming mouse adopts power-saving.When moving the mouse in wireless mode, the RGB lighting will automatically turn off. Turn off a part lights.Toggle the switch on the bottom of the mouse to the middle, it will turn off a part RGB lights(keeping wheel light and LOGO light on)</span></li>\r\n</ul>','/upload/6e9bd09d-8de3-4f4d-b956-ea0e55765635175352992197412.jpg','SM802 White Wireless Gaming Mouse',800000,17,'sm802-white-wireless-gaming-mouse',0,_binary '',1),(28,'<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\">\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Mini portable 60% compact layout: MK-BOX is a 68 keys mechanical keyboard have cute small size, but with separate arrow keys and F1-F12, Fn function keys you need, can use it for gaming or work while saving space.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Mechanical red switch: characterized for being linear and smoother, slight key sound has no paragraph sense with minimal resistance, but fast action without a tactile bump feel which makes it easier to tap the keyboard.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Classic charming blue LED backlit: Customize multiple illuminated LED light effects, supports about 15 backlight modes, press Fn + Ins can control it, FN + &larr;/&rarr; control backlight speed, FN + &uarr;/&darr; control backlight brightness.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Full anti-ghosting keyboard: all 68 keys are no conflict, black grey red mash up design, ergonomic suspension double-color injection keycap, double kickstand feet adjustable typing angle and detachable usb cable, both practical and beautiful.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Extensive compatibility: MageGee MK-Box mechanical keyboards use USB 2.0 connector making it compatible with Windows (2000, XP, ME, Vista, 7, 8), Linux and Mac, plug and play, no drivers or software required.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','/upload/64459dc7-26a7-43a8-a0a3-801f0bfb185317535300678414.jpg','MageGee Portable 60% Mechanical Gaming Keyboard',1600000,21,'magegee-portable-60-mechanical-gaming-keyboard-28',0,_binary '',2),(29,'<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\">\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Crisp Red SwitchExperience precise tactile feedback with our red switches, delivering smooth linear actuation perfect for rapid keystrokes in gaming and extended typing sessions. The satisfying click-free design minimizes fatigue while maintaining responsiveness, ensuring 87 full anti-ghosting keys register every command flawlessly&mdash;ideal for competitive gameplay and productivity.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Immersive RGB Lighting &amp; Premium BuildElevate your setup with dynamic rainbow backlighting featuring 6 vibrant LED modes (breathing, wave, reactive, etc.) and adjustable brightness. The sleek black metal frame adds durability and modern flair, complementing any desktop aesthetic. Customize lighting profiles to match your mood or gaming style effortlessly.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Compact &amp; Space-Saving DesignOptimized for portability and efficiency, the tenkeyless 87-key layout frees up desk space without sacrificing functionality. Perfect for small setups or on-the-go gamers, its lightweight build easily fits into backpacks while retaining full gaming-grade performance.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Beginner-Friendly Mechanical ExperienceDesigned for casual gamers and mechanical keyboard newcomers, this plug-and-play model balances affordability with premium features. Enjoy the signature \"mechanical feel\" for typing comfort and gaming precision, backed by